# Build context is the repo root for the frontend images (they need shared/),
# so keep heavy / irrelevant trees out of the context sent to the daemon.
**/node_modules
**/dist
**/.next
**/*.tsbuildinfo
**/*.log
.git
**/.env
**/.env.*
**/Dockerfile
**/.dockerignore
README.md
bench
aws-blocks
aws-microservices
